description:
We are excited to announce the final meetup of the year for the end of November.

We have two brilliant speakers lined up who will be coming out with their talk write-ups this week.

We are between a few locations at the moment but as always, it'll be central bristol, commutable from Temple Meads and kicking off at 6:30pm.

Details:

📍 - TBC
🗓️ 30th November
🕠 18:30 kick off
📢 Presentation Event
🍕🍺/🥤 Pizza and Beer/Soft drinks will be provided

To join the LinkedIn group, head to the link [here](https://www.linkedin.com/company/devops-cloud-native/)
